{"tid":713680,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"雷軍：因財務記賬上的原因，實際上小米去年是賺錢的","createTime":"2018-06-23T04:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T16:00:15.000Z","uid":9136,"like":68,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"8bc685ade8adf4ce5de3f1be866688da9b82204d","tid":713680,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:47:15.000Z","msg":"雷軍解釋了為什麼招股書顯示小米去年虧損嚴重的問題，他稱這是因為財務記賬上的原因，<br />\n實際上小米去年是賺錢的，凈利潤達到54億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【雷軍：小米去年營收突破1000億，同比增速67.5%】<br />\n<br />\n雷軍在發布會上介紹了小米去年的財報，小米去年的收入1146億人民幣，營收突破1000億人民幣。<br />\n而且去年的同比增速是67.5%，這一個增速在全球大型公司裡面排第二位。<br />\n在互聯網公司裡面排第一位。同時去年小米利潤是54億人民幣。今年一季度繼續高速增長89.5%，一季度利潤17億人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無事喇 原來係盈利既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二隻騰訊唔買就走寶喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"016c6ce3468d3a72629fc1cb7a3959901ff293d8","tid":713680,"uid":68094,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:48:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"399889d6dee880a643c0caac1d70b2d99be8c8eb","tid":713680,"uid":44171,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:52:01.000Z","msg":"返正可以任寫, 點解唔寫成賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb468341aa170fe3557e2aef146a30d0c317a02","tid":713680,"uid":13663,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/125229_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F125229_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4f61172f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f746575c670fbf42c731734b28bc700a1ae0c80c","tid":713680,"uid":9136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"399889d6dee880a643c0caac1d70b2d99be